channel.title: Multiple Teleports
channel.description: I hate the teleports in my client so I'm going to redo them, but I need to be able to list more than 1 teleport under a teleport. For instance when I click on PKing Teleports it opens up that lava thing with 4 different teleports or make it like glory where there's a list of teleports in chatbox. Thanks for the help.
